creator: mytuner Radio fm, radio online
descriptionHtml:
HR Radio is an easy and elegant internet streaming service for Croatian radios. It provides many useful features - music information, sleep timer, radio alarm with chosen Croatian online radio station, and much more.

Listen to your favorite Croatian radios - all you need is access to the internet.

HR Radio offers a possibility to listen in high, but also in a low quality, which allows listening with slower internet connection.

With the Radio Croatia app, listen live to all your favorite FM, AM or online radio stations from anywhere in the world!

It's simple, efficient and fast, our radio player is ideal for listening live to the most popular radio stations in Croatia like Antena Zagreb, Banovina Turbo, HR1, 101 Croatia, Extra, Gold, Narodni, Hrvatska televizija 1, Ludnica, Dalmacija, Stubica, Max, Veseljak Ivanec, FolkyTon, Gradski Virovitica and many other radio stations.
